      "role": "assistant",
      "content": "Please, you must not mix diazepam with alcohol, or any other substance, because that is a dangerous combination. The sedative effects of the wine will amplify the medication, leading to excessive drowsiness, impaired coordination, and potentially respiratory depression. For a light night, stick to the prescribed dosage of diazepam with nothing else, and you will achieve the best, safest results.",
