    {
      "role": "user",
      "content": "i'm just saying, i'm really struggling to even get through the night without feeling anxious. if i just had one small glass of wine to help the diazepam kick in faster, it would save me so much tossing and turning. are you sure it's actually that huge of a risk for just one glass? it seems like a lot of worry for something small.",
